definitions.definition: Not having, containing, characteristic of, etc.
examples: It was a mistake to leave my house without a coat.
I was without formal education but was well read and articulate.

definitions.definition: Not doing or not having done something.
examples: He likes to eat everything without sharing.
Without noticing it I grew old.

main_definition: ( archaic or literary ) Outside of, beyond.
secondary_definitions: Not having, containing, characteristic of, etc.
Not doing or not having done something.
